## ğŸ”‘ Quick Reference

### Colors
* âœ… Single color: `[red]text[/]`
* âœ… With background: `[white on red]text[/]`
* âœ… With style: `[bold green]text[/]`
* âœ… Combined: `[bold white on red]ALERT[/]`
* âœ… Multiple tags: `[cyan]Info[/] [red]Error[/]`

### Tables
* âœ… Rich-style: `table.add_column("Name", style="bold")`
* âœ… Rich markup: `table.add_column("[white on blue]Status[/]")`
* âœ… Column colors: `table.set_cols_color(["r", "g", "b"])`
* âœ… Row colors: `table.set_rows_color(["green", "yellow", "red"])`
* âœ… Styling rows: `table.add_row(..., style="bold red")`

